reviewText: This is a "must-have" video for all of those who enjoyed classic television.  Imagine a time when you could actually leave a child of any age in front of the TV while you went about your household chores or took a phone call.  No need to worry about wardrobe malfunctions or swearing.  This video is classic Jack Benny -- a video filled with laughs for the entire family to enjoy together.
I'm too young to know who Jack Benny was.  I was actually confused with Henny Youngman.  But the transaction was timely in the late days before Christmas.  My father in-law enjoyed the gift.
